flowchart TD
    %% ================================================================
    %% TownHelp — Provider Discovery Query Flow
    %% The most performance-critical query path in the application
    %% ================================================================

    A[User searches: maid Madhapur] --> B[service_categories]
    B -->|slug = 'maid'| C[provider_services]
    C -->|JOIN category_id, is_active = true| D{Parallel filters}

    D --> E[service_areas]
    D --> F[provider_profiles]

    E -->|area_name = 'Madhapur'| G[Matched providers in area]
    F -->|is_available = true, is_verified = true, deleted_at IS NULL| H[Active verified providers]

    G --> I[Intersection: providers matching both filters]
    H --> I

    I --> J[Sort by rating_avg DESC, completed_bookings DESC]
    J --> K[Return paginated results]
